Package: DXMeSH
Type: Package
Title: Generate PubMed Search Queries with MeSH Terms
Version: 1.1.1
Author: DaXuan <daxuan111000@163.com>
Maintainer: DaXuan <daxuan111000@163.com>
Description: The DXMeSH package helps users generate search queries for PubMed.
    Given a set of keywords, it fetches the associated MeSH terms and constructs
    a PubMed search query. The search query can be used in PubMed to search for
    relevant articles.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
